== 评价 ==
2016年1月27日，Google宣布平台第19个月，Cardboard发货量超过500萬个，上架的兼容应用超过1000个，安装次数达2500多万次。公司介绍，期间用户观看了超过35万小时的YouTube VR视频，50万名学生通过Expeditions计划进行VR实地考察<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.androidcentral.com/more-5-million-google-cardboard-viewers-have-shipped-over-25-million-cardboard-apps-downloaded|title=Google: 5 million Cardboard viewers shipped, 25 million VR apps downloaded|work=Android Central|publisher=Mobile Nations|first=Jared|last=Dipane|date=2016-01-27|accessdate=2016-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160712090805/http://www.androidcentral.com/more-5-million-google-cardboard-viewers-have-shipped-over-25-million-cardboard-apps-downloaded|archive-date=2016-07-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theverge.com/2016/1/27/10842438/google-shipped-5-million-cardboard-headsets|title=Google has shipped over 5 million Cardboard headsets|work=The Verge|publisher=Vox Media|first=Micah|last=Singleton|date=2016-01-27|accessdate=2016-01-27|archive-date=2021-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127024001/https://www.theverge.com/2016/1/27/10842438/google-shipped-5-million-cardboard-headsets|dead-url=no}}</ref>。到2017年3月，发货量突破1000万，应用程序下载量超过1.6亿次<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.androidcentral.com/google-has-shipped-10-million-cardboard-vr-headsets-2014|title=Google has shipped 10 million Cardboard VR headsets since 2014|work=Android Central|publisher=Mobile Nations|first=Harish|last=Jonnalagadda|date=2017-03-01|accessdate=2017-03-01|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807063658/https://www.androidcentral.com/google-has-shipped-10-million-cardboard-vr-headsets-2014|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

Cardboard的成功说服Google开发更先进的虚拟现实硬件并任命新的虚拟现实主管<ref>{{cite web | url = http://blogs.wsj.com/digits/2016/01/12/alphabet-appoints-new-virtual-reality-chief/ | website = Wall Street Journal | title = Alphabet Appoints New Virtual-Reality Chief | date = 2016-01-12 | last1 = Nicas | first1 = Jack | accessdate = 2016-02-12 | archive-date = 2020-08-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200801081954/https://blogs.wsj.com/digits/2016/01/12/alphabet-appoints-new-virtual-reality-chief/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2016年5月18日，Google在I/O大会上公布了名为[[Google_Daydream|Daydream]]的增强型VR平台<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theverge.com/2016/5/18/11683536/google-daydream-virtual-reality-announced-android-n-io-2016|title=Daydream is Google’s Android-powered VR platform|work=The Verge|publisher=Vox Media|first1=Adi|last1=Robertson|first2=Ross|last2=Miller|date=2016-05-18|accessdate=2016-05-18|archive-date=2020-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201222015319/https://www.theverge.com/2016/5/18/11683536/google-daydream-virtual-reality-announced-android-n-io-2016|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

